    <item>
      <title>美国欢迎塞尔维亚能源转型以抵御克里姆林宫的影响</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-11/us-embraces-serbia-s-energy-shift-to-fend-off-kremlin-influence</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国国务院一位高级外交官在访问巴尔干国家期间表示，美国将支持塞尔维亚减少对俄罗斯化石燃料进口的依赖并加快向可再生能源转型。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-11/us-embraces-serbia-s-energy-shift-to-fend-off-kremlin-influence</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 11 Oct 2024 15:08:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Meloni 官员急于在意大利预算截止日期前增加收入</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-11/meloni-officials-rush-to-raise-revenue-for-italy-budget-deadline</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士透露，意大利总理乔治亚·梅洛尼 (Giorgia Meloni) 的政府正面临着最后一刻寻找新方法来增加收入的紧迫任务，因为它试图为向意大利选民承诺的赠款提供资金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-11/meloni-officials-rush-to-raise-revenue-for-italy-budget-deadline</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 11 Oct 2024 14:55:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国对 iPhone 城台湾员工涉嫌行贿展开调查</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-11/china-probes-four-taiwan-staff-at-hon-hai-for-alleged-bribery</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据北京台办消息，中国政府部门正在调查苹果公司主要组装合作伙伴鸿海精密工业股份有限公司的四名台湾员工，他们涉嫌涉及行贿等犯罪行为。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-11/china-probes-four-taiwan-staff-at-hon-hai-for-alleged-bribery</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 11 Oct 2024 14:55:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>卢拉扩大所得税豁免范围，巴西雷亚尔下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-11/brazil-s-real-sinks-as-lula-floats-bigger-income-tax-exemptions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴西总统路易斯·伊纳西奥·卢拉·达席尔瓦表示，他希望对工资不超过 5,000 雷亚尔（893 美元）的工人提供超出现有承诺的更大范围的所得税减免，这加剧了投资者对财政政策的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-11/brazil-s-real-sinks-as-lula-floats-bigger-income-tax-exemptions</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 11 Oct 2024 14:21:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>双重风暴将气候问题推入美国总统竞选</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-11/double-punch-storms-thrust-climate-into-the-us-presidential-race</link>
      <description><![CDATA[飓风海伦和米尔顿的袭击使得应对气候灾害成为竞选最后几周的一个主要议题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-11/double-punch-storms-thrust-climate-into-the-us-presidential-race</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 11 Oct 2024 13:20:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>莫桑比克民众等待选举结果，但可信度受到质疑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-11/mozambicans-await-election-results-as-opposition-cries-foul</link>
      <description><![CDATA[莫桑比克选举当局继续汇总周三大选的结果，反对党候选人维南西奥·蒙德拉内 (Venâncio Mondlane) 指控投票日以及随后的计票过程中存在大量违规行为。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-11/mozambicans-await-election-results-as-opposition-cries-foul</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 11 Oct 2024 11:07:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列加强对贝鲁特的打击，但尚未与伊朗通话</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-11/israel-yet-to-reach-iran-decision-as-it-steps-up-beirut-strikes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据一名以色列官员称，以色列尚未决定如何对上周伊朗的导弹袭击进行报复，并且仍然受到美国和其他国家的压力，要求其限制报复的严厉程度。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-11/israel-yet-to-reach-iran-decision-as-it-steps-up-beirut-strikes</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 11 Oct 2024 06:58:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国重启与瑞士贸易谈判 力推“全球化英国”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-11/uk-resumes-trade-talks-with-switzerland-in-global-britain-push</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国和瑞士贸易谈判代表将于周一恢复贸易谈判，双方寻求促成更深层次的彼此金融服务市场准入，以及达成数据共享和工人签证方面的协议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-11/uk-resumes-trade-talks-with-switzerland-in-global-britain-push</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 11 Oct 2024 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亚洲安全峰会前夕，巴基斯坦枪手杀害 20 名矿工</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-10-11/urgent-gunmen-kill-20-miners-and-wound-others-in-an-attack-in-southwest-pakistan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴基斯坦奎达（美联社） — 一名警方官员周五表示，枪手在巴基斯坦西南部杀死了 21 名矿工，造成 6 人受伤，当局对此予以谴责，并开始搜寻袭击者。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-10-11/urgent-gunmen-kill-20-miners-and-wound-others-in-an-attack-in-southwest-pakistan</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 11 Oct 2024 02:48:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
